#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Font Viewer"
msgstr "字体查看器"

#. Tag: author
#: index.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Burkhard.Lueck; &Burkhard.Lueck.mail;"
msgstr "&Burkhard.Lueck; &Burkhard.Lueck.mail;"

#. Tag: trans_comment
#: index.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "ROLES_OF_TRANSLATORS"
msgstr "Guo Yunhe, Tyson Tan"

#. Tag: date
#: index.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "2018-03-31"
msgstr "2018-03-31"

#. Tag: releaseinfo
#: index.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plasma 5.12"
msgstr "Plasma 5.12"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "fontview"
msgstr "字体视图"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "fonts"
msgstr "字体"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kfontview; is an application to view and install different types of fonts:"
msgstr "&kfontview; 是一款用于查看和安装各种类型字体的应用程序："

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "&TrueType; (<filename class=\"extension\">.ttf</filename>)"
msgstr "&TrueType; (<filename class=\"extension\">.ttf</filename>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"OpenType (<filename class=\"extension\">otf</filename>, <filename class="
"\"extension\">.ttf</filename>)"
msgstr ""
"OpenType (<filename class=\"extension\">otf</filename>, <filename class="
"\"extension\">.ttf</filename>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&PostScript; type 1 (file extension on &Windows; &amp; OS/2 <filename class="
"\"extension\">.pfb</filename>/<filename class=\"extension\">.pfm</filename>; "
"on &UNIX;/&Linux; <filename class=\"extension\">.pfa</filename>/<filename "
"class=\"extension\">.afm</filename>)"
msgstr ""
"&PostScript; 类型 1 (文件扩展名在 &Windows; &amp; OS/2 上为 <filename class="
"\"extension\">.pfb</filename>/<filename class=\"extension\">.pfm</filename>；"
"在 &UNIX;/&Linux; 上为 <filename class=\"extension\">.pfa</filename>/"
"<filename class=\"extension\">.afm</filename>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"BDF (Bitmap Distribution Format, file extension <filename class=\"extension"
"\">.bdf</filename>)"
msgstr ""
"BDF (Bitmap Distribution Format (位图分发格式)，文件扩展名为 <filename class="
"\"extension\">.bdf</filename>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"PCF (Portable Compiled Format, file extension <filename class=\"extension\">."
"pcf</filename>)"
msgstr ""
"PCF (Portable Compiled Format (可移植已编译格式)，文件扩展名为 <filename "
"class=\"extension\">.pcf</filename>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use it as standalone program to preview and install a font "
"downloaded from the Internet. In the preview you can check that the font has "
"all characters you need."
msgstr ""
"本程序可以作为一款独立程序用于预览和安装从互联网下载的字体。您可以在预览视图"
"中检查字体是否包含您需要的所有字符。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kfontview; can be launched from the &systemsettings; module "
"<ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/fontinst/index.html\"> <guilabel>Font "
"Management</guilabel></ulink> to use the extended preview capabilities of "
"&kfontview;."
msgstr ""
"KDE 字体查看器还可以从系统管理对话框的 <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/fontinst/"
"index.html\"><guilabel>字体管理</guilabel></ulink> 页面启动，在此状态下可以使"
"用它的扩展字体预览功能。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively you can use the <guilabel>Font Management</guilabel> module to "
"install, remove, preview and manage all fonts on your system."
msgstr ""
"您也可以使用 <guilabel>字体管理</guilabel> 模块来安装、移除、预览和管理系统中"
"的所有字体。"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kfontview; application</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kfontview; 应用程序</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kfontview; application</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kfontview; 应用程序</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kfontview;'s <guilabel>Standard Preview</guilabel> displays your font in "
"several different sizes using a pangram (a sentence using every letter of "
"the alphabet at least once). So you can get a good idea of what it will look "
"like. From the drop down box in the toolbar you can choose additional "
"preview types:"
msgstr ""
"&kfontview; 的 <guilabel>标准预览</guilabel> 使用一个全字母句 (每个字母在句子"
"中至少出现一次，不过中日韩字体只能展示尽可能多的部首/笔画) 显示字体在不同大小"
"的效果。所以你可以知道它安装启用后将是什么显示效果。从工具栏的下拉框，您可以"
"选择额外的预览类型："

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>All Characters</guilabel> displays all characters provided by the "
"font in one size."
msgstr "<guilabel>所有字符</guilabel> 以统一大小显示字体提供的所有字符。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unicode Block: The Unicode standard arranges groups of characters together "
"in blocks"
msgstr "Unicode 区块：根据 Unicode 标准将字符按区块分组展示"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unicode Script: In Unicode, a script is a collection of letters and other "
"written signs used to represent textual information in one or more writing "
"systems"
msgstr ""
"Unicode 脚本：在 Unicode 中，脚本指的是是一个或多个书写系中用来表示文字和书写"
"符号的集合"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Change Text</guibutton>: Using this button opens the "
"<guilabel>Preview String</guilabel> dialog where you can insert a user "
"defined text. This feature enables you to check that a font supports the "
"characters you need."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>更改文本</guibutton>：使用此按钮打开 <guilabel>预览字符串</"
"guilabel> 对话框，您可以在那里插入用户定义的文本。 此功能允许您检查字体是否支"
"持您需要的字符。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the zoom buttons or the mousewheel to change the font size in "
"all preview types."
msgstr "您可以使用缩放按钮或鼠标滚轮来更改所有预览类型的字体大小。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <guilabel>Unicode Block</guilabel> and <guilabel>Unicode Script</"
"guilabel> preview mode additional tooltip info's are displayed hovering a "
"character with the mouse pointer: The character's Unicode "
"<guilabel>Category</guilabel> and the value in <guilabel> UCS-4</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>UTF-16</guilabel>, <guilabel>UTF-8</guilabel> and as <guilabel>XML "
"Decimal Entity</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"在 <guilabel>Unicode 块</guilabel>和 <guilabel>Unicode 脚本</guilabel>预览模"
"式中，鼠标指针在字符上悬停时将显示额外的工具提示信息：字符的 Unicode "
"<guilabel>分类</guilabel>和<guilabel> UCS-4</guilabel> 中的值、"
"<guilabel>UTF-16</guilabel>、 <guilabel>UTF-8</guilabel> 和 <guilabel>XML 十"
"进制实体</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To install a font you downloaded from the Internet, click the "
"<guibutton>Install</guibutton> button in the lower-right corner."
msgstr ""
"要安装您从互联网下载的字体，请点击右下角的 <guibutton>安装</guibutton> 按钮。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can install the font for personal us only available to you or system-"
"wide available for all users, the latter will require administrator "
"privileges."
msgstr ""
"您可以为安装仅供您使用的字体或让系统内所有用户使用，后者将需要管理员权限。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fonts are often provided in an archive format like <literal role=\"extension"
"\">zip</literal>. Open these archives with &ark; which provides a simple "
"previewer for fonts. To make use of the extended capabilities of &kfontview; "
"extract the fonts and open them in &kfontview;."
msgstr ""
"字体通常会被打包为压缩文件格式，例如 <literal role=\"extension\">zip</"
"literal>。您可以使用 &ark; 打开这些压缩文件，它也内建了简单的字体预览功能。要"
"使用 &kfontview; 的全部功能，您必须先把字体从压缩文件中解压出来，然后使用 "
"&kfontview; 打开它们。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applications need to be restarted to use of the newly installed fonts."
msgstr "需要重新启动应用程序才能使用新安装的字体。"
